---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="AI Readiness Assessment"
  description="AI Readiness Assessment to evaluate your organization's AI maturity, use-case readiness and operating model alignment for strategic AI adoption."
>

  <section class="section-py bg-[#05070D]" aria-labelledby="assessment-heading">
    <div class="container-site">

      <nav class="mb-8" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/" class="text-white/40 text-sm hover:text-white/65 transition-colors">
          ← Facundo Gangemi
        </a>
      </nav>

      <span class="eyebrow">AI Assessment</span>

      <h1 id="assessment-heading" class="text-section font-heading font-bold text-white mt-2 mb-6 max-w-[22ch]">
        AI Readiness Assessment
      </h1>

      <p class="text-white/65 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-[56ch] mb-6">
        Before investing in AI at scale, organizations need a clear picture of their
        AI maturity, use-case readiness and operating model alignment. The AI Readiness
        Assessment evaluates where your organization stands and what needs to change
        for AI adoption to deliver strategic outcomes.
      </p>

      <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed max-w-[56ch] mb-12">
        The assessment covers AI strategy clarity, data and technology readiness, governance
        structures, organizational capabilities, and the operating model conditions needed
        to embed AI sustainably. Outcomes include a prioritized view of gaps and a
        structured AI adoption roadmap. Contact to discuss the assessment for your organization.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">
          Discuss the Assessment
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/advisory/ai-adoption" class="btn-outline">Explore AI Adoption Advisory</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
